25. Block vs Inline Elements
Block Elements

Take full width.

Examples:

div
p
h1
section
article
table
Inline Elements

Take only needed width.

Examples:

span
a
img
strong
em
26. Div and Span
Div

Block container.

<div>
Span

Inline container.

<span>
27. HTML Metadata
<meta>

Examples:

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="description">
<meta name="keywords">
<meta name="author">
<meta name="viewport">
28. Responsive Design Meta Tag
<meta name="viewport"
content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
29. HTML APIs

HTML5 introduced APIs.

Geolocation API

Gets user location.

