Move elements.

Web Storage API

Stores data.

Web Workers

Background processing.

History API

Browser history manipulation.

30. Local Storage vs Session Storage
Feature	Local	Session
Lifetime	Permanent	Until tab closes
Size	~5MB	~5MB
Access	Same origin	Same origin
