42. HTML Interview Questions (Theory)
What is HTML?

A markup language used to structure web pages.

Difference between HTML and HTML5?

HTML5 introduced semantic tags, multimedia support, APIs, local storage, canvas, SVG, etc.

Difference between div and span?
div = block element
span = inline element
Difference between id and class?
id = unique
class = reusable
Difference between GET and POST?
GET sends data via URL.
POST sends data in request body.
What is Semantic HTML?

HTML elements that describe their meaning.

Example:

<header>
<footer>
<article>
<nav>
